  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Instalao de the Xfce4 Pulseaudio Plugin</title>

    <para>
      Install the <application>Xfce4 Pulseaudio Plugin</application> by running
the following commands:
    </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure --prefix=/usr &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Esse pacote no vem com uma sute de teste.
    </para>

    <para>
      Agora, como o(a) usurio(a) <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem>:
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

